Go inside a snow globe using the Polycam app! 3D scanning -> 3D printing is just too much fun. No worries if you don’t own a printer (although now a days you can buy a 3D printer for less than $100) there are online services like shapeways.com that will print the model for you, even in full color if you want! Just make sure it’s the right size for your snowglobe. I got my kit off Amazon and I already had some paint so I decided to paint the model myself. Even if you don’t want a snowglobe, printing and painting a model of anything you scan with Polycam is a super fun activity and a great way to make personalized gifts. Have fun!
